Introduction

Uhm Jungwoo, also known as Jungwoo, is a singer and actress from South Korea. She used to be in a group called BVNDIT. She joined the group on March 12, 2019, and they debuted with the song "BVNDIT, Be Ambitious!" on April 10, 2019.

But on November 11, 2022, BVNDIT disbanded after their contracts ended. Then, in April 2023, Jungwoo signed up with ShowPLAY ACTORS to start acting in musicals.
